structures.label: Caspar Schwenckfeld, Von der Herrlichkeit Christi

description: CCCC MS 338, written in a German script of the sixteenth century, contains a copy of Von der Herrlichkeit Christi by Caspar Schwenckfeld (or Kaspar von Schwenkfeld of Ossig) (1489/90-1561). Schwenckfeld was a Reformation theologian from Silesia and his writings formed the bases for a Protestant group known as the Schwenkfelders.
